					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Most of the code looks okay, though I see at least two things that could cause problems:<br /><br />1. You should wait until VBLANK before enabling rendering in your &quot;Housekeeping&quot; section, otherwise you'll get a glitched-out half frame.<br />2. You should set your scroll ($2000/$2005/$2005) <strong>before</strong> enabling rendering ($2001), though this should only be an issue if you were mid-frame above.</div>

					
