					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The positions of pointer low and pointer high need to be reversed. 6502 is little endian, with the low byte coming first in RAM addresses.<br /><br />Simple fix...<br /><br />.rsset $0000<br />bg_ptr_low .rs 1 ; bg pointer low byte<br />bg_ptr_hi .rs 1 ; bg pointer high byte<br /><br /><br />with no other changes. might work.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://nesdoug.com" class="postlink">nesdoug.com</a> -- blog/tutorial on programming for the NES</div>
